snippet: Mourners lined the streets of Sarajevo on Tuesday as trucks carried the remains of 409 newly identified victims of the  Srebrenica massacre to their final resting place.
abstract: Thousands of mourners line streets of Sarajevo as trucks carry remains of 409 newly identified victims of 1995 Srebrenica massacre to their final resting place in village of Potocari.
